## Endpoints

```
# Streams  [auth.jwt]
GET    /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams                                       ListStreamsController
POST   /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams                                       CreateStreamController
GET    /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams/{stream}                              ShowStreamController
PATCH  /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams/{stream}/schedule                     ScheduleStreamController
PATCH  /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams/{stream}/start                        StartStreamController
PATCH  /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams/{stream}/end                          EndStreamController
PATCH  /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams/{stream}/archive                      ArchiveStreamController
POST   /api/v1/rooms/{room}/streams/{stream}/destinations                 AddStreamDestinationController
```

